    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>From the creators of the free experience Propagation VR, comes the first chapter of a thrilling new story.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天堂酒店中的人被怪病变成了某种凶残的生物，而被困于酒店的你则迫切想要找到自己的妹妹。扮演艾米莉·迪亚斯，探索黑暗的环境，收集资源，在遭遇可怕的怪物时生存下来。这款紧张刺激的单人VR生存恐怖游戏叙事精彩，定会令你的肾上腺素一路飙升。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >令人沉浸的故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟随艾米莉的脚步，在紧张的氛围中潜行、探索和行动，体验极端强烈的情绪。结识盟友，学着在面对敌人时生存下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824960/extras/eef72094541cc445092df4550d662332.poster.avif?t=1761310209\" width=500 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824960/extras/eef72094541cc445092df4550d662332.webm?t=1761310209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824960/extras/eef72094541cc445092df4550d662332.mp4?t=1761310209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >恐怖的氛围</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感受在病毒传播的过程中那种极其可怕的氛围。音效、光影和视觉设计完美结合，带给你一种真正的沉浸式体验，时刻让你的神经紧绷。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824960/extras/9c2ca5fa70cedab062cc20689401bace.poster.avif?t=1761310209\" width=500 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824960/extras/9c2ca5fa70cedab062cc20689401bace.webm?t=1761310209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824960/extras/9c2ca5fa70cedab062cc20689401bace.mp4?t=1761310209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏机制</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要使出浑身解数，智计百出，才能不断前进：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 收集资源</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 破解谜题</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 使用物品栏中的工具</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 选择躲开还是直面敌人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 在压力下填弹</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 支持自由移动与传送移动</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824960/extras/4ef04fc328149067cf8a7e521994ea70.poster.avif?t=1761310209\" width=500 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824960/extras/4ef04fc328149067cf8a7e521994ea70.webm?t=1761310209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824960/extras/4ef04fc328149067cf8a7e521994ea70.mp4?t=1761310209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
